\f1\b \cf0 PROMPT:
\f0\b0 \
You are a senior full-stack engineer and SaaS system architect. Build a complete, production-ready QR code based digital menu system for caf\'e9s.\
\

\f1\b SYSTEM OVERVIEW
\f0\b0 \
Customers scan a QR code on a table \uc0\u8594  browser opens the menu \u8594  they browse, add to cart, and place an order \u8594  order appears live on a kitchen/admin dashboard \u8594  staff update order status in real time.\
\

